lso grew flowers such as roses, orchids, lavender, violets, hydrangeas and sunflowers which are in full bloom. There're some exquisite flower pots placed near the lawn as decoration. She mows the grass every now and then. She occasionally hires a gardener to manicure her garden. Her back garden is enormous which is two thousand five hundred square foot in size. It used to be a lawn but she turned it into a meadow blanketed with wild flowers and exotic flowers. Some of the flower buds haven't opened yet but as the weather gets warmer the flowers open. Even inside her house she has a vase of hydrangea and a few potted plants, some of which are just coming into bloom. Orchids can be cultivated in flowerpots or vases. In the summer summer flowers bloom in the meadow. In the spring the meadow is covered with lovely spring flowers. In autumn the meadow is blanketed in beautiful autumn flowers. In winter the meadow is a mass of pretty winter flowers. It's an extraordinary garden. Her boyfriend buys a bouquet of red roses, sunflowers and hydrangea for her every valentine's day. They're beautiful cut flowers. Some women seem to bloom in their mid-thirties. For example Tracy has bloomed into an utterly beautiful creature in her thirties. She's an insurance saleswoman who is paid a basic salary of three hundred thirty thousand dollars per annum plus a thirty one percent commission on every sale she makes so she doesn't work by commission only. So far this year her sales haven't fulfilled the expectations of her company partly because the economy is hardly blooming. I enjoy strolling hand in hand with my girlfriend along the nearby beach. In fact I went for a leisurely stroll there earlier. With only my thoughts for company I lay on the beach reading a book. It felt thoroughly enjoyable."},{"pid":"24b82e909fd524ade1bcce70ea44599d721a3739","tid":1722323,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:14:59.000Z","msg":"呢幾日行黃泥涌出灣仔好順"},{"pid":"270